title: Last10 x64 v2 RS1 Pro ~TEST~
description:
* TEST VERSION ONLY *

This version of Last10 is only being released as a test to see if it is able to work for anyone as I have problems with it getting a black screen on boot after the first reboot from the desktop, to repair this reboot a few times and use the advanced recovery options to do a startup repair, this has fixed the problem for me some of the time, please respond if you use this so I can continue working on a solution or complete the existing mod if the ratio of success is more than I am expecting.

Please keep a backup of your data and a image of a working Windows OS that you can restore if this fails to boot to the desktop after a reboot and MS update/reboot. This will save you time and effort
